Repeat: sl 1 wyif, k2, sl 1 wyif, k3
sl 1 wyib, k2, sl 1 wyib, k3
sl 1 wyif, k2, sl 1 wyif, k3

drop first slipped stitch off needle to front of work, slip next 2 stitches to right hand needle, drop 2nd slip stitch off needle to front of work; then pick up the 1st dropped stitch with left-hand needle, slip the same 2 stitches back to the left hand needle, then with right hand needle pick up the second dropped stitch and replace it on left-hand needle; k7
